        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Justice for Exploited Children Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill replaces the current maximum civil penalty of $11,000 for a violation of the child labor laws with a minimum civil penalty of $5,000 and a maximum of $132,270 (or, in the case of a violation that causes death or serious injury, $25,000 and $601,150, respectively).&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
